#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is a small program to practice calculating with fractions and "
"percentages. Different exercises are provided for this purpose and you can "
"use the learning mode to practice with fractions. The program checks the "
"user's input and gives feedback."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; je majhen program za vadbo računanja z ulomki in odstotki. V ta "
"namen so na voljo različne vaje in način učenja lahko uporabite za vadbo z "
"ulomki. Program preveri uporabnikov vnos in poda povratne informacije."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
