#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is a small program to practice calculating with fractions and "
"percentages. Six different exercises are offered as well as a learning mode."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; je majhen program za vadbo računanja z ulomki in odstotki. Na voljo "
"je šest različnih vaj in način učenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Arithmetic</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to solve a given "
"fraction task. You have to enter the numerator and the denominator. This is "
"the main exercise."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Aritmetika</guilabel> - v tej vaji morate rešiti dano nalogo z "
"ulomki. Vnesti morate števec in imenovalec. To je glavna vaja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Comparison</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to compare the "
"size of 2 given fractions, using the symbols <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>&lt;</guibutton> or <guibutton>=</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Primerjava</guilabel> - v tej vaji morate primerjati velikost dveh "
"danih ulomkov z uporabo simbolov <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, <guibutton>&lt;"
"</guibutton> ali <guibutton>= </guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Conversion</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to convert a "
"given number into a fraction."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pretvorba</guilabel> - v tej vaji morate dano število pretvoriti v "
"ulomek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Mixed Numbers</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to convert a "
"mixed number into an improper fraction (ratio) and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Mešana števila</guilabel> - v tej vaji morate pretvoriti mešano "
"število v nepravilen ulomek (razmerje) in obratno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Factorization</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to factorize "
"a given number into its prime factors."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Faktorizacija</guilabel> - v tej vaji morate dano število "
"faktorizirati na prafaktorje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Percentage</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to calculate "
"percentages."
msgstr "<guilabel>Odstotek</guilabel> - v tej vaji morate izračunati odstotke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In each different exercise &kbruch; will generate a task and the user has to "
"solve it. The program checks the input and gives a feedback about it."
msgstr ""
"V vsaki drugi vaji &kbruch; bo ustvaril nalogo in uporabnik jo mora rešiti. "
"Program preveri vnos in o njem poda povratno informacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; counts how many tasks were solved at all and how many tasks were "
"solved correctly. The statistics are shown to the user."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; šteje, koliko nalog je bilo sploh rešenih in koliko nalog je bilo "
"pravilno rešenih. Statistika je prikazana uporabniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is very compact and focuses on the core idea of a task generator. "
"An online help system provides context-sensitive help for the different "
"situations."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; je zelo kompakten in se osredotoča na osnovno idejo generatorja "
"opravil. Spletni sistem pomoči nudi kontekstno občutljivo pomoč za različne "
"situacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kbruch;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kbruch;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the mode: learning or exercises"
msgstr "Izbira načina: učenje ali vaje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &kbruch;, it offers you two modes: <guilabel>Exercise</"
"guilabel> which is the training mode and <guilabel>Learning</guilabel> where "
"you can understand fractions. Clicking one of the pictures will enter the "
"chosen mode. Here is a screenshot of &kbruch;'s mode choices:"
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &kbruch;, vam ponudi dva načina: <guilabel>Vaja</guilabel>, ki "
"je način usposabljanja, in <guilabel>Učenje</guilabel>, kjer lahko razumete "
"ulomke. S klikom na eno od slik vstopite v izbrani način. Tukaj je posnetek "
"zaslona izbire načina &kbruch;:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kbruch; mode choices</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kbruch; možnosti načina</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kbruch; mode choices</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kbruch; izbire načina</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click one of the picture to choose the mode."
msgstr "Kliknite eno od slik, da izberete način."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Exercise Screen"
msgstr "Glavni zaslon za vadbo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of &kbruch;'s main Exercise screen:"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona glavnega zaslona &kbruch; za vadbo:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbruch; main screen, directly after the exercise start"
msgstr "&kbruch; glavni zaslon, neposredno po začetku vadbe"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbruch; main screen"
msgstr "&kbruch; glavni zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All exercises take place in this screen. This ensures that &kbruch; is easy "
"to use even for young users! The main screen is separated into 5 parts: "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para> the menubar with the 3 menus <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu>, <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> </para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para> the toolbar, where you can switch between the "
"different exercises </para></listitem> <listitem><para> the "
"<guilabel>Options:</guilabel> on the left, where you can define the "
"difficulty and various settings for the tasks </para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para> the task part, where you have to enter the result of the "
"given task </para></listitem> <listitem><para> the statistical part, where "
"you can see how many tasks have been solved correctly or attempted </para></"
"listitem> </itemizedlist> At any time, you can go back to Modes using the "
"<guiicon>Back</guiicon> icon in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Vse vaje potekajo na tem zaslonu. To zagotavlja, da &kbruch; je enostaven za "
"uporabo tudi za mlade uporabnike! Glavni zaslon je razdeljen na 5 delov: "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para> menijska vrstica s 3 meniji "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>, <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> </para></listitem> <listitem><para> orodna vrstica, "
"kjer lahko preklapljate med različnimi vajami </para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para> <guilabel>Možnosti:</guilabel> na levo, kjer lahko določite "
"težavnost in različne nastavitve za naloge </para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para> del naloge, kjer morate vnesti rezultat dane naloge </"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para> statistični del, kjer lahko vidite, koliko "
"nalog je bilo pravilno rešenih ali poskusnih </para></listitem> </"
"itemizedlist> Kadar koli se lahko vrnete na načine z uporabo <guiicon>Nazaj</"
"guiicon> ikona v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can hide the <guilabel>Options:</guilabel> section by dragging it to the "
"left."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek <guilabel>Možnosti:</guilabel> lahko skrijete tako, da ga povlečete "
"v levo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First you have to choose an exercise in the toolbar. Default is "
"<guilabel>Arithmetic</guilabel>. The task part will change according to the "
"chosen task. Some settings in the <guilabel>Options</guilabel> section will "
"be enabled, depending on the task you have chosen."
msgstr ""
"Najprej morate izbrati vajo v orodni vrstici. Privzeto je "
"<guilabel>Aritmetika</guilabel>. Del nalog se spreminja glede na izbrano "
"nalogo. Nekatere nastavitve v razdelku <guilabel>Možnosti</guilabel> bodo "
"omogočene, odvisno od opravila, ki ste ga izbrali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will find an icon to generate a new task in the toolbar as well. This "
"action is also available in the menu <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This action is always "
"enabled. If you have not solved the currently given task, a new task is "
"generated and the statistics are set back."
msgstr ""
"V orodni vrstici boste našli tudi ikono za ustvarjanje novega opravila. To "
"dejanje je na voljo tudi v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To dejanje je vedno "
"omogočeno. Če trenutno dane naloge niste rešili, se ustvari nova naloga in "
"statistika se vrne nazaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you terminate &kbruch; the currently chosen exercise will be saved and "
"restored on next startup."
msgstr ""
"Če prekinete &kbruch; trenutno izbrana vaja bo shranjena in obnovljena ob "
"naslednjem zagonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statistical Part"
msgstr "Statistični del"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kbruch; statistics</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kbruch; statistika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kbruch; statistics</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kbruch; statistika</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this part of the main screen you can see:"
msgstr "V tem delu glavnega zaslona lahko vidite:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "on the left, how many tasks have been solved"
msgstr "na levi, koliko nalog je bilo rešenih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "on the right, in green, how many tasks have been solved correctly"
msgstr "desno z zeleno barvo koliko nalog je bilo pravilno rešenih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "on the right, in red, how many tasks have been solved incorrectly"
msgstr "na desni z rdečo barvo koliko nalog je bilo napačno rešenih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "on the right, in orange, how many tasks have been skipped"
msgstr "na desni oranžno koliko nalog je bilo preskočenih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reset the statistics by clicking on the <guimenu>New</guimenu> "
"button in the toolbar or choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Statistiko lahko ponastavite s klikom na gumb <guimenu>Novo</guimenu> v "
"orodni vrstici ali izbiro <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The statistics will be saved when &kbruch; is closed and restored on next "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"Statistika bo shranjena, ko bo &kbruch; se zapre in obnovi ob naslednjem "
"zagonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kbruch; appearance"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kbruch; videz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this dialog you can adjust some general settings for the task display. To "
"open this dialog use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kbruch;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko prilagodite nekatere splošne nastavitve za "
"prikaz opravil. Če želite odpreti to pogovorno okno, uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kbruch;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kbruch; settings dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kbruch; pogovorno okno z nastavitvami</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kbruch; settings dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kbruch; pogovorno okno z nastavitvami</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two sections to adjust the setting:"
msgstr "Obstajata dva razdelka za prilagoditev nastavitve:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Colors</guilabel>: Choose the colors for the different parts of a "
"mathematical expression: numbers, operational sign, fraction bar."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Barve</guilabel>: Izberite barve za različne dele matematičnega "
"izraza: številke, operacijski znak, ulomek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Fonts</guilabel>: Choose a font for displaying the task."
msgstr "<guilabel>Pisave</guilabel>: izberite pisavo za prikaz naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings will be saved on &kbruch;'s termination and restored on the "
"next startup."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve bodo shranjene ob prekinitvi &kbruch; in obnovljene ob naslednjem "
"zagonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Learning Screen"
msgstr "Glavni zaslon za učenje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kbruch; learning mode</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kbruch; način učenja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kbruch; learning mode</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kbruch; način učenja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the <guibutton>Hint</guibutton> button toggles the display of the "
"help on the right which explains you how the rings work."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Namig</guibutton> preklopite prikaz pomoči na "
"desni, ki vam pojasni, kako delujejo obroči."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exercises"
msgstr "Vaje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exercise Arithmetic"
msgstr "Vaja Aritmetika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this exercise you have to solve a given task. Therefore you have to enter "
"the integer part of a fraction and the numerator and the denominator. The "
"difficulty of the generated task can be adjusted by using some options on "
"the left."
msgstr ""
"V tej vaji morate rešiti dano nalogo. Zato morate vnesti celo število ulomka "
"ter števec in imenovalec. Težavnost ustvarjene naloge je mogoče prilagoditi "
"z uporabo nekaterih možnosti na levi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several parameters which influence the difficulty of the generated "
"tasks:"
msgstr "Obstaja več parametrov, ki vplivajo na težavnost generiranih nalog:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Question:"
msgstr "Vprašanje:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:341 index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mixed number:"
msgstr "Mešano število:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set if the fractions will appear as mixed numbers or not in the question "
"expression ( mixed number example: 1 4/5 = 9/5 )."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite, ali bodo ulomki v izrazu vprašanja prikazani kot mešana števila "
"ali ne (primer mešanega števila: 1 4/5 = 9/5)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of terms:"
msgstr "Število izrazov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of terms (separate fractions) given in each task. From 2 to 5, "
"inclusive."
msgstr ""
"Število izrazov (ločenih ulomkov), podanih v vsaki nalogi. Od 2 do vključno "
"5."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximum denominator:"
msgstr "Največji imenovalec:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The highest number &kbruch; will use as the main denominator in the tasks it "
"sets. From a minimum of 10 to a maximum of 50."
msgstr ""
"Največje število &kbruch; bo uporabljal kot glavni imenovalec pri nalogah, "
"ki jih zastavlja. Od najmanj 10 do največ 50."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Answer:"
msgstr "Odgovor:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set if the fractions will appear as mixed numbers or not in the answer "
"( mixed number example: 1 4/5 = 9/5 )."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite, ali bodo ulomki v odgovoru prikazani kot mešana števila ali ne "
"(primer mešanega števila: 1 4/5 = 9/5)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reduced Form:"
msgstr "Zmanjšana oblika:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this to force the use of the reduced form."
msgstr "Označite to, da vsilite uporabo pomanjšane oblike."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operations:"
msgstr "Operacije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Operations which should be used in the task: <guilabel>Addition:</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Subtraction:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Multiplication:</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Division:</guilabel>. Check all operations you want to use."
msgstr ""
"Operacije, ki jih je treba uporabiti v nalogi: <guilabel>Seštevanje:</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Odštevanje:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Množenje:</guilabel> "
"ali <guilabel>Deljenje:</guilabel>. Označite vse operacije, ki jih želite "
"uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have changed the parameters you have to click on the <guimenu>New</"
"guimenu> button in the toolbar to generate a task which uses the new "
"parameters. You can also call this action from the menubar with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. This will reset the statistics. To avoid that, click the "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton> button to proceed with the changed parameters."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste spremenili parametre, morate v orodni vrstici klikniti gumb "
"<guimenu>Novo</guimenu>, da ustvarite nalogo, ki uporablja nove parametre. "
"To dejanje lahko pokličete tudi iz menijske vrstice z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. To bo ponastavilo statistiko. Da bi se temu izognili, kliknite "
"gumb <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>, da nadaljujete s spremenjenimi parametri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The chosen parameters will be saved on &kbruch;'s termination and restored "
"on next startup."
msgstr ""
"Izbrani parametri bodo shranjeni ob prekinitvi &kbruch; in obnovljeni ob "
"naslednjem zagonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Solving Tasks"
msgstr "Reševanje nalog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have solved a given task, you need to enter the result into the "
"three input boxes. In the left box you enter the integer part of the "
"fraction, in the upper box the numerator and in the lower box the "
"denominator. If the option <guilabel>Mixed number:</guilabel> in the "
"<guilabel>Answer:</guilabel> section is unchecked, the left box for the "
"integer part of the fraction is hidden. Then you use only the numerator box "
"and the denominator box for your input."
msgstr ""
"Ko rešite dano nalogo, morate rezultat vnesti v tri vnosna polja. V levo "
"okence vpišeš celoštevilski del ulomka, v zgornje polje števec in v spodnje "
"polje imenovalec. Če možnost <guilabel>Mešano število:</guilabel> v razdelku "
"<guilabel>Odgovor:</guilabel> ni potrjena, je levo polje za celoštevilski "
"del ulomka skrito. Nato za vnos uporabite samo polje za števec in polje za "
"imenovalec."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the result is negative, you can enter a minus sign in front of the "
"numerator or denominator. If the result is 0, just type a 0 in the numerator "
"input field. If the result has a denominator of 1, you can leave the lower "
"box empty."
msgstr ""
"Če je rezultat negativen, lahko pred števec ali imenovalec vnesete znak "
"minus. Če je rezultat 0, samo vnesite 0 v polje za vnos števca. Če ima "
"rezultat imenovalec 1, lahko spodnje polje pustite prazno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have entered the result you should click the <guibutton>Check</"
"guibutton> button below the input boxes. &kbruch; will check your input and "
"present the correct result on the right below the <guilabel>Incorrect!</"
"guilabel> string:"
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete rezultat, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Preveri</guibutton> pod poljem "
"za vnos. &kbruch; bo preveril vaš vnos in prikazal pravilen rezultat na "
"desni pod nizom <guilabel>Nepravilno!</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Checked Task</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Preverjeno opravilo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Checked Task</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Preverjeno opravilo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This task was solved incorrectly. The correct value is shown in 2 different "
"forms: normal (reduced) and mixed number."
msgstr ""
"Ta naloga je bila napačno rešena. Pravilna vrednost je prikazana v dveh "
"različnih oblikah: normalno (zmanjšano) in mešano število."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you checked the <guilabel>Reduced form:</guilabel> in the Options in the "
"<guilabel>Answers:</guilabel> section then you always have to enter the "
"result reduced. &kbruch; will show you a short message like the one in the "
"screenshot below, if you enter the correct result unreduced. The answer will "
"then be counted as incorrect."
msgstr ""
"Če ste označili <guilabel>Zmanjšani obrazec:</guilabel> v Možnostih v "
"razdelku <guilabel>Odgovori:</guilabel>, morate vedno vnesti pomanjšan "
"rezultat. &kbruch; vam bo prikazal kratko sporočilo, kot je tisto na "
"spodnjem posnetku zaslona, če vnesete pravilen nezmanjšan rezultat. Odgovor "
"bo potem štel kot nepravilen."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Unreduced Result</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nezmanjšan rezultat</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Unreduced Result</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nezmanjšan rezultat</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To continue with the next task, click on the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> "
"button. If you want to change the parameters for the next task please do "
"this before clicking on the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nadaljevati z naslednjo nalogo, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>. Če želite spremeniti parametre za naslednjo nalogo, naredite to, "
"preden kliknete gumb <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Exercise Comparison</title>"
msgstr "<title>Primerjava vaj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this exercise you have to compare 2 given fractions. You have to choose "
"the bigger fraction of both by selecting the correct comparison sign."
msgstr ""
"V tej vaji moraš primerjati 2 podana ulomka. Izbrati morate večji del obeh z "
"izbiro pravilnega primerjalnega znaka."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Exercise Comparison</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primerjava vaj</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Exercise Comparison</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primerjava vaj</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First choose the correct comparison sign. After you have chosen the "
"comparison sign, the result will show on the right. A green square with "
"<guilabel>Correct!</guilabel> will tell you that your answer was correct "
"while a red square with <guilabel>Incorrect!</guilabel> will indicate that "
"your answer was wrong. You will get to the next task by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite pravi primerjalni znak. Ko izberete primerjalni znak, se na "
"desni prikaže rezultat. Zeleni kvadrat z <guilabel>Pravilno!</guilabel> vam "
"bo povedal, da je bil vaš odgovor pravilen, medtem ko bo rdeči kvadrat z "
"<guilabel>Napačno!</guilabel> nakazal, da je bil vaš odgovor napačen. Na "
"naslednjo nalogo boste prišli s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this exercise only the option <guilabel>Mixed number:</guilabel> is "
"enabled. If checked the fractions will appear as mixed numbers."
msgstr ""
"V tej vaji je omogočena le možnost <guilabel>Mešano število:</guilabel>. Če "
"je označeno, bodo ulomki prikazani kot mešana števila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Exercise Conversion</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pretvorba vaj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this exercise you have to convert a given number into a fraction. You "
"have to enter numerator and denominator."
msgstr ""
"V tej vaji morate dano število pretvoriti v ulomek. Vnesti morate števec in "
"imenovalec."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Exercise Conversion</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pretvorba vadbe</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Exercise Conversion</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pretvorba vaj</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side of the equal sign in the screenshot above you can see a "
"recurring decimal. This means, that the fraction shown as a decimal has a "
"repeating part. The repeating part is marked with the small bar above the "
"numbers. Those numbers repeat ad infinitum."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani znaka enačaja na zgornjem posnetku zaslona lahko vidite "
"ponavljajočo se decimalko. To pomeni, da ima ulomek, prikazan kot decimalka, "
"ponavljajoči se del. Ponavljajoči se del je označen s črtico nad številkami. "
"Te številke se ponavljajo v neskončnost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549 index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have entered the numerator and denominator click on the "
"<guibutton>Check</guibutton> button. &kbruch; will check your input and "
"present the correct result. After this step you will get to the next task by "
"clicking on the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste vnesli števec in imenovalec, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Preveri</"
"guibutton>. &kbruch; bo preveril vaš vnos in predstavil pravilen rezultat. "
"Po tem koraku boste prišli do naslednje naloge s klikom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556 index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not forget to enter the result reduced. Unreduced results will be counted "
"as solved not correctly."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite vnesti zmanjšanega rezultata. Nezmanjšani rezultati bodo šteti "
"kot nepravilno rešeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:562 index.docbook:605 index.docbook:652 index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this exercise all options are disabled."
msgstr "V tej vaji so vse možnosti onemogočene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Exercise Mixed Numbers</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vaja Mešana števila</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this exercise you have to convert a given mixed number into an improper "
"fraction (ratio) and vice versa. You have to enter numerator and denominator "
"for improper fraction or a whole number, numerator and denominator for mixed "
"number."
msgstr ""
"V tej vaji morate dano mešano število pretvoriti v nepravilen ulomek "
"(razmerje) in obratno. Vnesti morate števec in imenovalec za nepravilen "
"ulomek ali celo število, števec in imenovalec za mešana števila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Exercise Mixed Numbers</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vaja mešanih števil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Exercise Mixed Numbers</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vaja mešanih števil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side of the equal sign in the screenshot above you can see a "
"mixed number. This means, that the number is made up of a whole number and a "
"proper fraction. You should enter the equal improper fraction (the numerator "
"part of such fraction is greater or equal to the denominator part)."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani znaka enačaja na zgornjem posnetku zaslona lahko vidite "
"mešano število. To pomeni, da je število sestavljeno iz celega števila in "
"pravega ulomka. Vnesite enak nepravi ulomek (številčni del takega ulomka je "
"večji ali enak imenovalcu)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Exercise Factorization</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vaja faktorizacije</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this exercise you have to factorize a given number into its prime "
"factors. You have to enter all prime factors of the number."
msgstr ""
"V tej vaji morate dano število razložiti na prafaktorje. Vnesti morate vse "
"prafaktorje števila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Exercise Factorization</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vaja faktorizacije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Exercise Factorization</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izvedite faktorizacijo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter a factor by clicking on the prime factor buttons. The "
"<quote>x</quote> sign is automatically inserted, when you click the next "
"prime factor button. You can remove the last entered prime factor by "
"clicking on the <guibutton>Backspace</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Faktor lahko vnesete s klikom na gumbe prafaktorja. Znak <quote>x</quote> se "
"samodejno vstavi, ko kliknete gumb naslednjega prafaktorja. Zadnji vneseni "
"prafaktor lahko odstranite s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Vračalka</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have entered all prime factors click on the <guibutton>Check</"
"guibutton> button. &kbruch; will check your input and present the correct "
"result. After this step you will get to the next task by clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete vse prafaktorje, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Preveri</guibutton>. "
"&kbruch; bo preveril vaš vnos in predstavil pravilen rezultat. Po tem koraku "
"boste prišli do naslednje naloge s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the screenshot at the top of this page you can see a <quote>x</quote> "
"between the prime factors. This is the multiplication sign. The product of "
"all prime factors must be the number you try to factorize."
msgstr ""
"Na posnetku zaslona na vrhu te strani lahko vidite <quote>x</quote> med "
"prafaktorjema. To je znak za množenje. Zmnožek vseh prafaktorjev mora biti "
"število, ki ga poskušate faktorizirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have to enter all prime factors even when a prime factor repeats several "
"times. Example: As prime factors of number 18 you have to enter 2, 3 and 3."
msgstr ""
"Vnesti morate vse prafaktorje, tudi če se prafaktor večkrat ponovi. Primer: "
"Kot prafaktorje števila 18 morate vnesti 2, 3 in 3."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Exercise Percentage</title>"
msgstr "<title>Odstotek vadbe</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this exercise you have to answer some percentage questions."
msgstr "V tej vaji morate odgovoriti na nekaj vprašanj o odstotkih."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Exercise Percentage</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Odstotek vadbe</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Exercise Percentage</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Odstotek vadbe</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have entered your answer click on the <guibutton>Check</guibutton> "
"button. &kbruch; will check your input and present the correct result. After "
"this step you will get to the next task by clicking on the <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete odgovor, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Preveri</guibutton>. &kbruch; "
"bo preveril vaš vnos in predstavil pravilen rezultat. Po tem koraku boste "
"prišli do naslednje naloge s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

